{"tid":1419214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日得閒既手足入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:34:49.000Z","uid":199137,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32e54da3a3af544347cc4008b7219f936e151f7c","tid":1419214,"uid":199137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:24:56.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得機場仲有手足頂緊<br />\n好多個post都講過機場好重要<br />\n一黎可以對外宣傳到宜家既香港<br />\n二黎班狗又唔敢入黎搞9我地<br />\n所以跪求大家得閒既 真係入去機場支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要返工既手足 放工入去行個圈都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP.S樓豬陣間會入<br />\n<br />\n其實宜家機場仲有手足架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418818</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"20ce66672d7a860023790ec53ba48b3562149b37","tid":1419214,"uid":199137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a47ef6d876388271affff965398b497e23abb069","tid":1419214,"uid":199137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"af1712f8e8397bce3af4fc966c0c46db15ba9205","tid":1419214,"uid":199137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1d69555985434a7563a2ee82df74037bf187835c","tid":1419214,"uid":264734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b3df44b4a947122111d43925743767a9ef07968","tid":1419214,"uid":199137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"348c433bed37175685b32d4b14dbc3f6066e1de0","tid":1419214,"uid":264734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3012a247516e33d2e30a4d2fd45382b7cbb4af77","tid":1419214,"uid":19913